            <div class="info cssanimation leFadeInLeft sequence">

        <p>Let's see some examples:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Reading an integer:</li>
            <pre><code>int num;
scanf("%d", &amp;num);</code></pre>
            <li>Reading a floating-point number:</li>
            <pre><code>float price;
scanf("%f", &amp;price);</code></pre>
            <li>Reading a string:</li>
            <pre><code>char name[50];
scanf("%s", name);</code></pre>
        </ul>
        <p>Make sure to include the appropriate format specifier based on the type of data you're reading.</p>
